2815,"db_to_form_package_schema() strips tracking summary, isopen",seanh,seanh,"If an IDatasetForm plugin with a db_to_form_schema() based on db_to_form_package_schema() (which is in turn based on default_package_schema()) is in use then the 'tracking_summary' dict and the 'isopen' bool get stripped from package dicts during validation, e.g. during package_show(), and these values are then not available to templates.",defect,new,awaiting triage,ckan-v1.8.1,ckan,,,,ckan,none
